  <brief_title>Early, Simple and Reliable Detection of Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension (PAH) in Systemic Sclerosis (SSc)</brief_title>
  <acronym>DETECT</acronym>
  <official_title>A Two-stage Prospective Observational Cohort Study in Scleroderma Patients to Evaluate Screening Tests and the Incidence of Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension and Pulmonary Hypertension</official_title>
